headline: Are You a Momentum Investor? This 1 Stock Could Be the Perfect Pick

headline: Dow Jones Futures Rise, CoreWeave Tumbles After Stock Market Runs On Fed
summary: The S&P 500 and Nasdaq hit highs as Fed rate cut odds rose on the CPI report. Meta led new buys. Nvidia-backed CoreWeave reported late.
